# Spring Batch Governance Automation

## Contract Expiry Batch

Daily scan:

```text
ACTIVE + endDate < today
↓
EXPIRED
↓
Audit
↓
Kafka Notification
```

## Approval Reminder Batch

Daily scan:

```text
PENDING > 48h
↓
Notify current approver
↓
Audit
```

## Approval Escalation Batch

Daily scan:

```text
PENDING > 5 days
↓
Escalate to Admin
↓
Audit
```

